.TH "nvme_init_set_features_err_recovery" 9 "nvme_init_set_features_err_recovery" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_set_features_err_recovery \- Initialize passthru command for Error Recovery
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_set_features_err_recovery
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u32 nsid "  ","
.BI "bool sv "  ","
.BI "__u16 tler "  ","
.BI "bool dulbe "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "nsid" 12
Namespace ID
.IP "sv" 12
Save value across power states
.IP "tler" 12
Time-limited error recovery value
.IP "dulbe" 12
Deallocated or Unwritten Logical Block Error Enable
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Set Features command with
FID value NVME_FEAT_FID_ERR_RECOVERY
